<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gasp1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gasp,</orth> subst. catch of breath; always applied to the agonies of death: <cit><quote>to the last g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.3.70" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 3, 70</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.127" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 127</bibl>. <cit><quote>at last g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.5.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 5, 53</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>my latter g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his latest g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.1.108" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 1, 108</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to the latest g.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.2.41" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 41</bibl></cit>.
